org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.PAM

Interface PaStep

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GaScenario, GaStep, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceUsage, TimedElement, TimedProcessing
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PaCommStep, PaRequestedStep
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PaCommStepImpl, PaRequestedStepImpl, PaStepImpl

    public interface PaStep
extends GaStep
    A representation of the model object 'Pa Step'.

    The following features are supported:

    • No Sync
    • Ext Op Demand
    • Ext Op Count
    • Behav Demand
    • Behav Count

    See Also:
    PAMPackage.getPaStep()
